'''FreiTek Incorporated'''<ref name="Geektionary">''[[Star Wars: Geektionary: The Galaxy from A - Z]]''</ref> was a manufacturing company that notably produced the [[E-wing starfighter|E-wing escort fighter]] for the [[New Republic Defense Fleet]]<ref name="Comprehensive" /> as well as the [[life support]] units used by the [[Resistance pilot]]s thirty [[Standard year|years]] after the [[Battle of Endor]].<ref name="TVD" />

